title: 210 - We Finally Get Our Hand on Smooth Cremux
description: Today’s episode of The POD kicks off with a FULL BARN and the long awaited Smooth Cremue!!! All the boys give an honest taste test of the Canadian deliciously and then jump right into the Pod FOD, which is a folder compiled of all things around the internet. Todays FOD includes Elon Musk’s gypsy tendencies, the new Thor trailer, Mexican pizza being brought back to Taco Bell, and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
